collectible.name: Scarcity: Water Faction Oldschool Ship
collectible.author: 0xe330dc28b47d73884ad88837aecfee1f49ad7e7b
collectible.description: These were the ships the water faction used before they were called this way. Although the gnomes had powerful machines to cross the ocean, Tilt knew, from the Old Tales of Scarcity, written by the first sailors, that the Atlantis would attack any technological ship they see.Tilt sailed for many months, around Origin City, until he found Fauna Island. In that time, it was empty and it was called the Seahorse Island, given its form, but it was the location under which the Atlantis lived.

collectible.name: Flora's Seagull (Scarcity and Flora Tales)
collectible.author: 0xe330dc28b47d73884ad88837aecfee1f49ad7e7b
collectible.description: Few people knows the story that links the babies and the seagulls, but it is a hard one. The seagulls were created by the immortal druids, in order to hunt babies IRL down to the sacrifice in the Altar of Sacrifice, in Flora's Island. Created by Egglion and branded and storytold by The Philosopher.

collectible.name: Cryptovoxels Sun (wearable)
collectible.author: 0xe330dc28b47d73884ad88837aecfee1f49ad7e7b
collectible.description: Created by Egglion and branded by The Philosopher, to be in the skies of Cryptovoxels, illuminating our life.

collectible.name: Scarcity: Fauna's Atlantis Tritons
collectible.author: 0xe330dc28b47d73884ad88837aecfee1f49ad7e7b
collectible.description: They are guardians of the secrets of the water, and they also are the keepers of the Atlantis' magical treasure. Give them a beer made of gold, and they will tell you the most interesting stories about the creation of the world. The Atlantis books have the oldest tales from the entire metaverse. Unfortunatly, only the Atlantis have a copy and they keep them as a secret, together with the Book of Prophecies. There is much to be revealed, and they know it all.

collectible.name: Scarcity: Atlantis
collectible.author: 0xe330dc28b47d73884ad88837aecfee1f49ad7e7b
collectible.description: Maybe only the Water Faction knows the real truth about the Atlantis. They are deep below the land that covers the bottom of the ocean. They guard their gold treasures with deep care because they use a gold machine in the neck to breath underwater. Given the mining capabilities of the gnomes, the water faction be Atlantis' friends and trade their mining work on Fauna for the Diamond of Days, which is a rare stone that could be used to power all the electrical instruments of many islands.

womp.author: 0x36354da80c30e3b1045ae2dd7640a99d12d7bcbb
womp.content: Flooded passage to Atlantis in Fauna from the CV underworld
